fix(scene): robust passage-note hook + add delete-scene-note

The passage double-click hook failed to install on Foundry v14 (Note class
resolution via foundry.canvas.placeables / global Note). Resolve the Note
placeable class via the canonical CONFIG.Note.objectClass (stable v10-v14)
with fallbacks, so double-clicking a targetScene pin navigates the GM.

Add delete-scene-note tool + delete-scene-notes module query: remove map pins
by id list or all of them, so pins can be re-placed/resized without re-importing
the scene (avoids the re-import churn that breaks cross-scene passage links).

Module v1.6.1.

